1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:11,537
=The Moment I Met You=

2
00:00:11,537 --> 00:00:15,000
=Episode 9=

3
00:00:15,439 --> 00:00:16,039
But,

4
00:00:17,079 --> 00:00:18,440
you have to promise me one thign.

5
00:00:20,760 --> 00:00:22,440
Never lie to me again, alright?

6
00:00:26,519 --> 00:00:28,679
Not every lie is told with ill intent.

7
00:00:29,239 --> 00:00:30,879
When we first got together,

8
00:00:31,199 --> 00:00:32,880
didn't you hide your true identity too?

9
00:00:38,240 --> 00:00:40,520
I'm sorry. I was on a mission,
so I couldn't tell you.

10
00:00:40,520 --> 00:00:43,119
I didn't want to get you into trouble.

11
00:00:45,880 --> 00:00:46,799
Rest assured,

12
00:00:47,280 --> 00:00:48,240
everything I've done

13
00:00:48,759 --> 00:00:50,159
has been for the sake of our love.

14
00:00:50,880 --> 00:00:51,640
I know.

15
00:00:52,759 --> 00:00:55,960
And I know the Squirrel is
out there committing crimes

16
00:00:56,880 --> 00:00:58,520
just to try and clear your name.

17
00:01:00,840 --> 00:01:04,079
Maybe you really do
have a history with them.

18
00:01:04,959 --> 00:01:08,200
Maybe Squire Mei really is
part of the underworld.

19
00:01:09,680 --> 00:01:10,599
But...

20
00:01:11,959 --> 00:01:13,000
none of that matters.

21
00:01:13,010 --> 00:01:14,319
What matters is that you trust me,

22
00:01:14,319 --> 00:01:15,990
and trust the Imperial Court
to deliver justice.

23
00:01:17,439 --> 00:01:18,040
Chang.

24
00:01:18,640 --> 00:01:21,480
No matter how much that Squirrel does,

25
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:24,040
or how much she claims to be a vigilante,

26
00:01:24,319 --> 00:01:25,799
she is still breaking the law.

27
00:01:28,959 --> 00:01:31,439
If you try to help her,

28
00:01:32,040 --> 00:01:33,239
you're doing her more harm.

29
00:01:34,159 --> 00:01:36,079
I hope you understand what I'm saying.

30
00:01:42,012 --> 00:01:43,800
(Coroner's Office)

31
00:02:01,239 --> 00:02:02,799
Western Datura.

32
00:02:16,680 --> 00:02:18,319
Western Datura.

33
00:02:18,759 --> 00:02:20,639
(Western Datura)
A slow-acting hallucinogen.

34
00:02:20,759 --> 00:02:23,199
It causes the victim
to gradually lose touch with reality,

35
00:02:23,210 --> 00:02:25,250
eventually leading to madness
and self-mutilation,

36
00:02:25,360 --> 00:02:26,599
or even suicide.

37
00:02:27,240 --> 00:02:28,280
Highly lethal.

38
00:02:28,759 --> 00:02:30,840
(Lethal once ingested)
There is no cure.

39
00:02:36,479 --> 00:02:37,439
It seems possible

40
00:02:38,360 --> 00:02:40,919
that Lin Xin'er died from a poison.

41
00:02:57,937 --> 00:03:00,250
(Nine-Tailed Fox, Hu Mei'er)

42
00:03:01,080 --> 00:03:01,800
It's you!

43
00:03:02,479 --> 00:03:03,479
Well, hello there.

44
00:03:04,400 --> 00:03:05,439
It's quite late.

45
00:03:06,520 --> 00:03:07,879
Where are you off to?

46
00:03:08,919 --> 00:03:10,159
I've done everything

47
00:03:10,439 --> 00:03:11,360
you asked.

48
00:03:11,680 --> 00:03:12,639
I'm going home.

49
00:03:14,800 --> 00:03:16,400
Why not stay a few more days?

50
00:03:16,879 --> 00:03:20,840
Let me show you a really good time.

51
00:03:21,439 --> 00:03:22,479
Besides,

52
00:03:23,120 --> 00:03:25,759
that final payment I promised

53
00:03:26,400 --> 00:03:27,800
hasn't been settled yet.

54
00:03:29,360 --> 00:03:30,319
Keep the money.

55
00:03:31,159 --> 00:03:31,879
Get out of my way.

56
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:36,360
Since you're being so heartless,

57
00:03:36,680 --> 00:03:40,280
allow me to give you a final send-off.

58
00:04:00,599 --> 00:04:01,240
(Chang.)

59
00:04:01,840 --> 00:04:04,759
(No matter how much that Squirrel does,)

60
00:04:05,120 --> 00:04:07,039
or how much
she claims to be a vigilante,

61
00:04:07,439 --> 00:04:08,840
she is still breaking the law.

62
00:04:09,560 --> 00:04:12,000
If you try to help her,

63
00:04:12,479 --> 00:04:13,680
you're doing her more harm.

64
00:04:14,680 --> 00:04:16,680
I hope you understand what I'm saying.

65
00:04:18,279 --> 00:04:20,120
(Could Buyu be on to something?)

66
00:04:21,480 --> 00:04:23,000
(Was he)

67
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:24,560
(trying to warn me?)

68
00:04:27,800 --> 00:04:28,519
Auntie.

69
00:04:28,959 --> 00:04:29,839
What is it?

70
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:32,399
You just did a stint in prison.

71
00:04:32,600 --> 00:04:33,950
Tell me you've finally seen sense.

72
00:04:36,920 --> 00:04:37,759
A little bit.

73
00:04:38,480 --> 00:04:39,319
Think about it.

74
00:04:39,519 --> 00:04:40,879
Even with me behind bars,

75
00:04:41,319 --> 00:04:43,120
Buyu never wavered.

76
00:04:43,199 --> 00:04:45,120
It just proves
I didn't choose the wrong man.

77
00:04:48,560 --> 00:04:49,800
What you should have realized

78
00:04:49,879 --> 00:04:51,439
is that you need to cut ties with him

79
00:04:51,439 --> 00:04:52,519
immediately.

80
00:04:54,879 --> 00:04:56,079
He's the reason

81
00:04:56,279 --> 00:04:58,199
Luo Wushuang got suspicious
in the first place.

82
00:04:58,439 --> 00:05:00,079
He's the reason you ended up in jail.

83
00:05:01,240 --> 00:05:03,920
It is your fault for exposing your skills
and making her think

84
00:05:03,920 --> 00:05:05,319
you're with the Sacred Hand Sect.

85
00:05:05,480 --> 00:05:06,800
That's why she came after me.

86
00:05:08,759 --> 00:05:10,279
Don't you dare talk back to me.

87
00:05:13,160 --> 00:05:14,399
Alright, alright.

88
00:05:14,800 --> 00:05:15,519
I get it.

89
00:05:15,519 --> 00:05:16,720
You're just worried about me.

90
00:05:17,360 --> 00:05:18,600
But even the most perfect plan

91
00:05:18,600 --> 00:05:19,920
has its flaws.

92
00:05:23,000 --> 00:05:23,800
Exactly!

93
00:05:24,160 --> 00:05:25,839
We only got through this

94
00:05:26,040 --> 00:05:27,680
by pure luck.

95
00:05:27,959 --> 00:05:29,160
But what about next time?

96
00:05:29,519 --> 00:05:31,079
What if it's even more dangerous?

97
00:05:31,759 --> 00:05:34,160
You have to break up with him.

98
00:05:36,730 --> 00:05:38,480
Mao Buyu is the man
I, Chu Yunchang, chose.

99
00:05:38,879 --> 00:05:40,319
I'm not letting him go that easily.

100
00:05:40,839 --> 00:05:41,639
Don't worry.

101
00:05:41,639 --> 00:05:42,560
I know what I'm doing.

102
00:05:44,712 --> 00:05:45,560
Chang.

103
00:05:45,959 --> 00:05:47,240
All these risks and trouble,

104
00:05:47,399 --> 00:05:48,920
just for one guy?

105
00:05:49,920 --> 00:05:51,360
Think of everything that's happened

106
00:05:51,639 --> 00:05:52,800
since you met him.

107
00:05:53,639 --> 00:05:54,560
But that just proves

108
00:05:54,560 --> 00:05:55,920
that I made the right choice.

109
00:05:56,110 --> 00:05:58,460
You know what they say
about catching fish in muddy water.

110
00:05:58,839 --> 00:06:01,000
This world has been quiet for too long.

111
00:06:01,360 --> 00:06:03,319
We need to stir the pot

112
00:06:03,319 --> 00:06:05,330
if we want to lure the big fish
out into the open.

113
00:06:07,400 --> 00:06:09,319
I can't help feeling
that dragging Luo Wushuang

114
00:06:09,439 --> 00:06:10,639
into this mess

115
00:06:10,920 --> 00:06:12,319
is far too dangerous.

116
00:06:12,680 --> 00:06:15,399
She already despises you.

117
00:06:17,120 --> 00:06:18,759
If I were easily frightened,

118
00:06:18,920 --> 00:06:21,120
I wouldn't be the Sect Leader
of the Sacred Hand Sect,

119
00:06:21,310 --> 00:06:23,560
nor would I have taken on
the hunt for the Sacred Token.

120
00:06:24,040 --> 00:06:25,040
Actually, I hope

121
00:06:25,120 --> 00:06:27,399
Luo Wushuang stirs the pot
as much as possible.

122
00:06:28,639 --> 00:06:30,680
It might be the only way to find

123
00:06:30,680 --> 00:06:32,879
whoever's actually holding
the real Sacred Token.

124
00:06:36,279 --> 00:06:37,759
I still have a bad feeling about this.

125
00:06:40,160 --> 00:06:41,360
Come on, give me a smile.

126
00:06:45,920 --> 00:06:49,279
(Loyalty to the Nation)
Deputy Mao Jixian of the Probe Corps

127
00:06:49,519 --> 00:06:50,560
has been negligent.

128
00:06:51,040 --> 00:06:52,759
His failure caused
key prisoner Lin Xin'er

129
00:06:52,839 --> 00:06:54,879
to lose her sanity during interrogation

130
00:06:55,199 --> 00:06:57,720
and ultimately
take her own life in court.

131
00:06:57,720 --> 00:06:58,240
Sister.

132
00:06:58,480 --> 00:07:00,160
Chief Mao's actions are inexcusable.

133
00:07:00,160 --> 00:07:03,160
However, in light of his family's
generations of service

134
00:07:03,260 --> 00:07:04,439
and merit to the Gate Bureau,

135
00:07:04,720 --> 00:07:06,600
his punishment is mitigated.

136
00:07:07,120 --> 00:07:08,040
Effective immediately,

137
00:07:08,399 --> 00:07:10,120
Mao Jixian is stripped of his rank.

138
00:07:10,310 --> 00:07:11,680
He remains on duty pending review.

139
00:07:17,120 --> 00:07:17,759
(Righteousness and Honor)
My dear.

140
00:07:21,160 --> 00:07:22,480
How is my father-in-law?

141
00:07:22,820 --> 00:07:24,279
I brought some pastries to visit him.

142
00:07:24,279 --> 00:07:25,639
Who asked for your fake sympathy?

143
00:07:26,279 --> 00:07:27,600
How is it fake?

144
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:29,519
I truly care about him.

145
00:07:30,040 --> 00:07:31,279
My father isn't seeing anyone.

146
00:07:31,279 --> 00:07:32,399
And neither am I.

147
00:07:33,920 --> 00:07:35,199
Darling, there's something...

148
00:07:35,199 --> 00:07:36,199
Enough, stop nagging.

149
00:07:36,279 --> 00:07:37,160
(Righteousness and Honor)
You're giving me a headache.

150
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:43,240
Yunchang!

151
00:07:44,480 --> 00:07:46,040
Our men found the body of the jailer,

152
00:07:46,040 --> 00:07:48,279
Jin Dian, outside the city.

153
00:07:49,519 --> 00:07:50,600
Who would have a reason

154
00:07:51,120 --> 00:07:52,920
to murder a man like Jin Dian?

155
00:07:55,959 --> 00:07:57,090
Unless it's about Lin Xin'er.

156
00:07:57,800 --> 00:08:01,279
Are you saying her death was a setup?

157
00:08:02,480 --> 00:08:06,199
But I was watching her day and night.

158
00:08:06,199 --> 00:08:07,959
Who could have poisoned her
under my nose?

159
00:08:12,120 --> 00:08:13,519
Don't you look at me.

160
00:08:13,519 --> 00:08:14,600
She was poisoned,

161
00:08:14,839 --> 00:08:15,839
not hexed.

162
00:08:16,040 --> 00:08:17,639
I'm not taking the fall for this.

163
00:08:20,079 --> 00:08:22,319
Aside from your Confusion Gu,

164
00:08:22,680 --> 00:08:25,279
what other toxins could
drive a person mad?

165
00:08:25,279 --> 00:08:26,439
There are plenty.

166
00:08:26,800 --> 00:08:29,600
Western Datura, for one.

167
00:08:30,120 --> 00:08:31,439
Western Datura?

168
00:08:31,439 --> 00:08:31,959
Exactly.

169
00:08:32,279 --> 00:08:33,159
That stuff

170
00:08:33,159 --> 00:08:35,480
is just as potent as my Confusion Gu.

171
00:08:35,480 --> 00:08:37,200
In the right doses,

172
00:08:37,799 --> 00:08:40,919
it can make someone
slowly lose their mind.

173
00:08:42,000 --> 00:08:43,279
Well, start investigating!

174
00:08:43,639 --> 00:08:44,279
On it!

175
00:09:00,240 --> 00:09:01,159
Nice place, isn't it?

176
00:09:01,240 --> 00:09:02,320
Director Liu,

177
00:09:02,919 --> 00:09:04,759
it's been a while, hasn't it?

178
00:09:04,759 --> 00:09:05,360
It has.

179
00:09:05,360 --> 00:09:06,600
I've been swamped lately.

180
00:09:06,600 --> 00:09:07,799
Since I'm finally free today,

181
00:09:07,799 --> 00:09:10,679
I brought a friend along
for some entertainment.

182
00:09:11,240 --> 00:09:11,799
After you.

183
00:09:12,799 --> 00:09:13,480
Sanhuai,

184
00:09:13,759 --> 00:09:15,960
are we going to have a drink
at a place like this?

185
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:18,399
Don't tell me you've never been
to one of these before.

186
00:09:19,520 --> 00:09:20,240
Come on, let's go.

187
00:09:20,240 --> 00:09:20,799
I...

188
00:09:21,399 --> 00:09:22,320
Director Liu,

189
00:09:22,679 --> 00:09:24,960
I've reserved the best seats
for you both.

190
00:09:25,039 --> 00:09:26,000
Right this way.

191
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:26,919
Come on.

192
00:09:27,039 --> 00:09:27,759
Come on!

193
00:09:31,200 --> 00:09:32,080
Sanhuai,

194
00:09:32,440 --> 00:09:33,360
I really feel

195
00:09:33,360 --> 00:09:34,440
out of place here.

196
00:09:34,679 --> 00:09:35,720
I think I'll head back.

197
00:09:37,799 --> 00:09:38,720
Anran,

198
00:09:39,159 --> 00:09:40,919
just relax and enjoy the show.

199
00:09:43,360 --> 00:09:44,120
Look!

200
00:09:44,480 --> 00:09:45,799
The Western dancers are here.

201
00:10:28,879 --> 00:10:30,039
(That scent is so familiar.)

202
00:10:34,679 --> 00:10:36,480
(Western Datura.)

203
00:10:39,840 --> 00:10:40,480
Miss,

204
00:10:40,759 --> 00:10:42,120
your scent is quite unique.

205
00:10:42,120 --> 00:10:44,120
May I get a closer scent?

206
00:10:46,200 --> 00:10:47,080
Sir,

207
00:10:47,799 --> 00:10:50,080
aren't you being a bit overeager?

208
00:10:50,679 --> 00:10:51,480
I just wanted...

209
00:10:54,159 --> 00:10:55,919
I just wanted to catch your scent.

210
00:10:57,759 --> 00:10:58,799
Listen to me, miss.

211
00:10:58,799 --> 00:11:00,000
What do you think you're doing?

212
00:11:00,840 --> 00:11:02,519
Trying to force yourself on her?

213
00:11:02,519 --> 00:11:04,440
I just wanted to catch her scent!

214
00:11:04,559 --> 00:11:05,679
Catch what?

215
00:11:06,000 --> 00:11:06,759
Drag him out!

216
00:11:06,759 --> 00:11:08,080
Just one sniff! One sniff!

217
00:11:08,080 --> 00:11:09,200
Move it! Faster!

218
00:11:09,519 --> 00:11:10,200
Out!

219
00:11:10,320 --> 00:11:11,799
Don't you know the rules here?

220
00:11:12,039 --> 00:11:13,279
Stop acting like a big shot.

221
00:11:13,799 --> 00:11:15,159
Trying to get a free feel?

222
00:11:15,320 --> 00:11:16,960
I think you're looking for a beating.

223
00:11:16,960 --> 00:11:17,799
Madam! Madam!

224
00:11:17,919 --> 00:11:19,039
He doesn't know any better.

225
00:11:19,200 --> 00:11:20,960
He didn't mean it, I swear!

226
00:11:20,960 --> 00:11:22,320
I have to see that beauty!

227
00:11:23,559 --> 00:11:25,120
You want to see my Mei'er?

228
00:11:25,559 --> 00:11:26,279
Fine.

229
00:11:26,919 --> 00:11:27,960
Show me the money.

230
00:11:28,200 --> 00:11:28,799
Money?

231
00:11:32,679 --> 00:11:33,559
Here, money!

232
00:11:35,919 --> 00:11:37,919
Are you treating me like a beggar?

233
00:11:38,480 --> 00:11:40,279
To see my Mei'er alone

234
00:11:41,720 --> 00:11:43,480
costs at least a thousand taels.

235
00:11:43,480 --> 00:11:44,360
A thousand taels?

236
00:11:46,559 --> 00:11:47,879
Do you have a thousand taels?

237
00:11:48,519 --> 00:11:49,440
Are you insane?

238
00:11:49,639 --> 00:11:51,360
If your wife finds out, you're dead meat!

239
00:11:51,360 --> 00:11:52,159
I don't care right now!

240
00:11:52,159 --> 00:11:52,759
Do you have the money?

241
00:11:52,759 --> 00:11:53,440
Give it to me, now!

242
00:11:53,440 --> 00:11:54,840
Stop touching me!

243
00:11:54,840 --> 00:11:57,120
I didn't bring that much on me!

244
00:11:58,840 --> 00:11:59,360
Listen.

245
00:11:59,360 --> 00:12:00,600
Can I put it on my tab?

246
00:12:01,159 --> 00:12:01,919
Enough talk.

247
00:12:01,919 --> 00:12:02,879
Throw him out!

248
00:12:03,360 --> 00:12:03,679
Move!

249
00:12:03,679 --> 00:12:04,559
- Wait!
- Faster!

250
00:12:04,559 --> 00:12:05,279
- I...
- Out!

251
00:12:05,440 --> 00:12:05,919
Wait.

252
00:12:05,919 --> 00:12:06,879
Hold on, this is...

253
00:12:07,559 --> 00:12:08,840
Look, Director Liu.

254
00:12:09,039 --> 00:12:11,039
What kind of trash
is this friend of yours?

255
00:12:11,039 --> 00:12:13,159
Who tries to start a tab
at Zuihong Parlor?

256
00:12:13,159 --> 00:12:14,039
Madam, I...

257
00:12:14,039 --> 00:12:16,039
I didn't expect him to be so bold.

258
00:12:17,879 --> 00:12:19,279
Pathetic.

259
00:12:24,039 --> 00:12:25,679
Absolute country bumpkin.

260
00:12:26,720 --> 00:12:28,000
That man

261
00:12:28,600 --> 00:12:30,159
doesn't look like your average customer.

262
00:12:31,519 --> 00:12:32,600
Look into him.

263
00:12:33,240 --> 00:12:34,679
Don't let some nobody

264
00:12:35,120 --> 00:12:36,759
ruin our grand plans.

265
00:12:37,039 --> 00:12:38,159
Understood, mistress.

266
00:12:44,519 --> 00:12:46,759
Recently, several sons
of wealthy families in the Capital

267
00:12:47,080 --> 00:12:48,519
have vanished without a trace

268
00:12:48,679 --> 00:12:50,000
after a night out on the town.

269
00:12:50,480 --> 00:12:51,960
Soon after, their families received

270
00:12:51,960 --> 00:12:54,600
letters in the victims' handwriting
demanding massive ransoms.

271
00:12:54,799 --> 00:12:56,320
But the men never return.

272
00:12:56,720 --> 00:12:58,080
Instead, more letters arrive

273
00:12:58,399 --> 00:13:00,159
every few days,
asking for even more money.

274
00:13:00,840 --> 00:13:02,559
Do you think they've been killed?

275
00:13:03,360 --> 00:13:04,720
But the families have confirmed

276
00:13:04,919 --> 00:13:07,440
that the handwriting is
definitely authentic.

277
00:13:07,759 --> 00:13:08,919
Typical kidnappings

278
00:13:09,399 --> 00:13:10,679
are crimes of opportunity

279
00:13:10,679 --> 00:13:12,080
targeting specific individuals.

280
00:13:12,639 --> 00:13:13,399
But this is

281
00:13:13,639 --> 00:13:15,759
systematic, large-scale abduction.

282
00:13:16,279 --> 00:13:18,639
These people are
far from ordinary criminals.

283
00:13:38,080 --> 00:13:38,639
My dear.

284
00:13:39,360 --> 00:13:40,159
I'm so sorry.

285
00:13:40,879 --> 00:13:43,360
I have to use the money
for your birthday present.

286
00:13:44,039 --> 00:13:44,919
But don't you worry.

287
00:13:45,399 --> 00:13:47,919
I'll save up for three more years

288
00:13:48,240 --> 00:13:49,600
and buy you an even better gift.

289
00:13:50,200 --> 00:13:53,320
"Save what you can,
spend what you must."

290
00:13:53,679 --> 00:13:54,360
Hu Mei'er.

291
00:13:54,720 --> 00:13:56,120
I'm going to see you again.

292
00:13:57,240 --> 00:13:58,120
Xu Anran!

293
00:13:58,399 --> 00:13:59,000
My dear!

294
00:13:59,279 --> 00:14:01,120
You're seeing Hu Mei'er
at the Zuihong Parlor?

295
00:14:01,120 --> 00:14:02,080
No, I'm not...

296
00:14:02,080 --> 00:14:03,960
I have a perfectly good reason
for going there!

297
00:14:03,960 --> 00:14:05,879
So you admit it?

298
00:14:05,879 --> 00:14:06,720
I didn't admit...

299
00:14:08,360 --> 00:14:09,639
Well, I did, but...

300
00:14:09,639 --> 00:14:11,159
But I...

301
00:14:11,159 --> 00:14:12,480
I can't believe you, Xu Anran!

302
00:14:12,840 --> 00:14:14,720
You act so quiet and decent,

303
00:14:15,000 --> 00:14:16,960
but you're doing something this
behind my back?

304
00:14:17,120 --> 00:14:17,919
You're shameless!

305
00:14:17,919 --> 00:14:19,000
I am not!

306
00:14:19,000 --> 00:14:20,080
Let me explain, my dear!

307
00:14:20,080 --> 00:14:21,320
There's nothing to explain!

308
00:14:21,480 --> 00:14:23,000
I never want to see your face again!

309
00:14:24,200 --> 00:14:24,799
My dear!

310
00:14:25,080 --> 00:14:25,919
Let me explain!

311
00:14:26,120 --> 00:14:26,720
Wait!

312
00:14:33,519 --> 00:14:35,159
My dear, you've forgiven me?

313
00:14:37,399 --> 00:14:38,720
Drop dead, you stinking man!

314
00:14:39,400 --> 00:14:40,559
I'm confiscating this money.

315
00:14:40,560 --> 00:14:42,770
You're not spending a single coin
on those other women.

316
00:14:44,440 --> 00:14:45,039
My dear!

317
00:14:45,120 --> 00:14:46,000
I'm divorcing you!

318
00:14:50,159 --> 00:14:51,600
Three years of savings,

319
00:14:52,600 --> 00:14:53,519
gone, just like that.

320
00:14:54,660 --> 00:14:56,510
How am I supposed
to go to the Zuihong Parlor?

321
00:15:11,639 --> 00:15:12,759
(Token)
Since it's come to this,

322
00:15:13,440 --> 00:15:15,399
I have no choice
but to take a desperate risk.

323
00:15:19,570 --> 00:15:22,000
Let's see who dares obstruct
the Gate Bureau's investigation!

324
00:15:22,362 --> 00:15:23,480
(Justice and Integrity)

325
00:15:23,480 --> 00:15:24,080
Anran?

326
00:15:24,440 --> 00:15:25,799
I heard you arguing with Rong.

327
00:15:26,440 --> 00:15:28,000
Are you still heading to Zuihong Parlor?

328
00:15:28,000 --> 00:15:29,440
I'm going there on official business.

329
00:15:30,919 --> 00:15:32,759
You're married,
and you're still going there?

330
00:15:32,759 --> 00:15:33,399
What?

331
00:15:33,919 --> 00:15:34,919
Is my sister not...

332
00:15:34,919 --> 00:15:36,600
Buyu, you've got it all wrong.

333
00:15:36,600 --> 00:15:38,159
Think about what you know of me.

334
00:15:38,159 --> 00:15:39,480
Am I really that kind of person?

335
00:15:39,770 --> 00:15:41,759
I'm going to Zuihong Parlor
to investigate a case.

336
00:15:42,200 --> 00:15:44,080
Since when is a coroner
also an investigator?

337
00:15:47,279 --> 00:15:50,440
Lin Xin'er's actual cause of death
was poisoning.

338
00:15:51,530 --> 00:15:52,639
She didn't die from trauma.

339
00:15:53,159 --> 00:15:55,559
The Commissioner told me
not to stir up any more trouble.

340
00:15:56,120 --> 00:15:58,279
Not even Wushuang knows about this.

341
00:15:58,840 --> 00:16:01,000
So, I've decided
to investigate it myself.

342
00:16:01,799 --> 00:16:03,120
What else have you found lately?

343
00:16:03,600 --> 00:16:06,159
I've discovered that
this Hu Mei'er at Zuihong Parlor

344
00:16:06,159 --> 00:16:07,279
is extremely suspicious.

345
00:16:08,730 --> 00:16:10,080
My recent investigation shows that

346
00:16:10,799 --> 00:16:13,279
every wealthy merchant
who went missing or was kidnapped

347
00:16:14,080 --> 00:16:15,240
had visited Zuihong Parlor.

348
00:16:17,480 --> 00:16:18,639
Zuihong Parlor?

349
00:16:24,575 --> 00:16:27,850
♪Grudges and regrets
are like strong wine♪

350
00:16:27,888 --> 00:16:30,763
♪Drink it down and let it go♪

351
00:16:31,263 --> 00:16:36,981
♪An empty cup for our love and hate♪

352
00:16:38,163 --> 00:16:41,483
♪Tears blur a fate I can't control♪

353
00:16:41,613 --> 00:16:44,533
♪Let's drink until dawn♪

354
00:16:45,701 --> 00:16:50,941
♪Behind this mask, I'll never lie♪

355
00:16:52,163 --> 00:16:54,556
♪Every reunion feels like the first♪

356
00:16:54,556 --> 00:16:58,206
♪This hidden smile will never fade♪

357
00:16:58,275 --> 00:17:01,765
♪One heart, standing by your side♪

358
00:17:01,863 --> 00:17:04,838
♪To the ends of time♪

359
00:17:04,838 --> 00:17:08,213
♪The moon traces your face♪

360
00:17:08,400 --> 00:17:11,988
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

361
00:17:11,988 --> 00:17:18,228
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

362
00:17:18,563 --> 00:17:21,778
♪A silent prayer in my soul♪

363
00:17:22,063 --> 00:17:25,601
♪Carrying my vow beneath the moon♪

364
00:17:25,888 --> 00:17:28,913
♪Hoping we never drift apart again♪

365
00:17:28,913 --> 00:17:32,013
♪On our way to forever♪

366
00:17:32,013 --> 00:17:35,863
♪The moon traces your face♪

367
00:17:35,863 --> 00:17:39,223
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

368
00:17:39,413 --> 00:17:45,373
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

369
00:17:46,450 --> 00:17:56,090
♪Just to be with you♪
